<lb n="0790b11" ed="B"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0790b1101" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">蛤古沓切蜊力脂切蛤蜊蚌屬</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>腎</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0790b1114" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">時忍均水藏也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>嚇</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0790b1121" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">正作諕虛訝切誑也</note></p></cb:def></entry></cb:div>
